text: Natasha Abigail Taylor (born 14 December 1969), known professionally as Natascha McElhone (), is an English actress. She was in Ronin (1998), The Truman Show (1998) and Solaris (2002). ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:British movie actors Category:British stage actors Category:British television actors Category:British voice actors Category:Actors from Surrey
